- Bet: bet is placed before first card is dealt/before game begins. Blackjack typically pays out 3:2 or 6:5. Blackjack pays 2:1
- Splitting: maximum is 4 times https://www.gambling.com/ca/online-casinos/strategy/blackjack-strategy-splitting-and-doubling-down-explained-28800
- Double Down https://www.gambling.com/ca/online-casinos/strategy/blackjack-strategy-splitting-and-doubling-down-explained-28800
- Insurance. When the dealer is showing an Ace and before they show their hole. Payoff 2:1
  card, a side-bet called insurance becomes available.
- Add command "advise" to make a suggestion on what action to take.
- Add command "book" to print the rules
- Add command "surrender" https://www.casinotop10.net/blackjack-surrender
